OL,3,CThree plead guilty to neglect over
OL,4,Celderly woman's care home fall
OL,6,FThree nursing home workers have
OL,7,Fpleaded guilty to offences after an 84-
OL,8,Fyear-old woman fell from a wheelchair
OL,9,Fshe was not strapped into and broke
OL,10,Fher leg.
OL,12,FShirley Froggett, 84, died of
OL,13,Fpneumonia in November 2018 at the New
OL,14,FLodge Nursing Home in Mickleover,
OL,15,FDerby, after suffering a broken femur
OL,16,Fin the fall weeks earlier.
OL,18,FMrs Froggett's wheelchair did not have
OL,19,Fa functioning lap belt when she fell.
