OL,3,CThree plead guilty to neglect over
OL,4,Celderly woman's care home fall
OL,6,FNakeeba Akhtar, 33, Amar Muneer, 47,
OL,7,Fand 37-year-old Prabina Thapa, entered
OL,8,Fguilty pleas at Derby Crown Court on
OL,9,FTuesday on what would have been the
OL,10,Ffirst day of their trial.
OL,12,FMuneer, of Blackpool Street, Burton-on-
OL,13,FTrent, who was a nurse at the home,
OL,14,Fadmitted a count of wilful neglect by
OL,15,Fa care worker between September 18 and
OL,16,FSeptember 21 2018.
