OL,3,CThree plead guilty to neglect over
OL,4,Celderly woman's care home fall
OL,6,FAkhtar, of St Chads Road, Stoke-on-
OL,7,FTrent, and Thapa, of Bartley Wilson
OL,8,FWay, Cardiff, who had been carers at
OL,9,Fthe home, both admitted perverting the
OL,10,Fcourse of justice by making false
OL,11,Fstatements between September 18 and
OL,12,FDecember 5 2018.
OL,14,FThe defendants are not alleged to have
OL,15,Fcaused the pensioner's death.
OL,17,FCare home manager Lindsey Foster, 43,
OL,18,Fof St John's Road, Stoke-on-Trent,
OL,19,Fpleaded guilty to perverting the
OL,20,Fcourse of justice at a previous court
OL,21,Fhearing.
