OL,3,CThree plead guilty to neglect over
OL,4,Celderly woman's care home fall
OL,6,FNew Lodge Nursing Care Ltd and Foster
OL,7,Fwere fined at Southern Derbyshire
OL,8,FMagistrates' Court in 2022 for failing
OL,9,Fto provide safe care and treatment to
OL,10,Fa resident.
OL,12,FA jury of six men and six women sworn
OL,13,Fin on Monday morning to try the
OL,14,Fdefendants was discharged by Judge
OL,15,FMartin Hurst after the guilty pleas
OL,16,Fwere entered.
OL,18,FThe defendants were told they will be
OL,19,Fsentenced on February 6 and granted
OL,20,Funconditional bail.
