OL,3,CThree plead guilty to neglect over
OL,4,Celderly woman's care home fall
OL,6,FDetective constable Natalie Barnett,
OL,7,Ffrom Derbyshire Police, read a
OL,8,Fstatement outside the court on behalf
OL,9,Fof Elaine Froggett, Mrs Froggett's
OL,10,Fdaughter-in-law.
OL,12,FThe statement said: "After seven long
OL,13,Fyears, the conclusion today means that
OL,14,Ffinally justice has been served.
OL,16,F"To hear the guilty pleas was an
OL,17,Fenormous relief.
