OL,6,F"On behalf of the family, finally, we
OL,7,Fhave the closure we deserve. Shirley
OL,8,Fdied in horrendous circumstances. May
OL,9,Fher soul now rest in peace.
OL,11,F"The people responsible now have their
OL,12,Fown conscience to deal with.
OL,14,F"Finally, I would like to say if you
OL,15,Fhave a loved one in care, stay
OL,16,Fvigilant and speak up for those who
OL,17,Fcannot speak for themselves."
